      "start": 5858,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2630
    },
    {
      "text": "I get a little bit jealous.",
      "start": 5860,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2631
    },
    {
      "text": "You know, I think back, and I was a handsome guy.",
